Foghorn.Data.Comp.Fundq

Description

This module defines the variable set for Compustat North America Fundamentals Quarterly (FUNDQ), represented as a GADT (FundqV). Each constructor corresponds to a named variable and is indexed by an EconType (e.g., Float_, Int_, Text_, Date_).
